  "root_text": {
    "dhp44:0.1": "Khuddakanikāya ",
    "dhp44:0.2": "Dhammapada ",
    "dhp44:0.3": "Pupphavagga ",
    "dhp44:0.4": "Pathavikathāpasutapañcasatabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp44:1": "Ko imaṁ pathaviṁ vicessati, ",
    "dhp44:2": "Yamalokañca imaṁ sadevakaṁ; ",
    "dhp44:3": "Ko dhammapadaṁ sudesitaṁ, ",
    "dhp44:4": "Kusalo pupphamiva pacessati. ",
    "dhp45:1": "Sekho pathaviṁ vicessati, ",
    "dhp45:2": "Yamalokañca imaṁ sadevakaṁ; ",
    "dhp45:3": "Sekho dhammapadaṁ sudesitaṁ, ",
    "dhp45:4": "Kusalo pupphamiva pacessati. ",
    "dhp46:0": "Marīcikammaṭṭhānikabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp46:1": "Pheṇūpamaṁ kāyamimaṁ viditvā, ",
    "dhp46:2": "Marīcidhammaṁ abhisambudhāno; ",
    "dhp46:3": "Chetvāna mārassa papupphakāni, ",
    "dhp46:4": "Adassanaṁ maccurājassa gacche. ",
    "dhp47:0": "Viṭaṭūbhavatthu ",
    "dhp47:1": "Pupphāni heva pacinantaṁ, ",
    "dhp47:2": "byāsattamanasaṁ naraṁ; ",
    "dhp47:3": "Suttaṁ gāmaṁ mahoghova, ",
    "dhp47:4": "maccu ādāya gacchati. ",
    "dhp48:0": "Patipūjikakumārivatthu ",
    "dhp48:1": "Pupphāni heva pacinantaṁ, ",
    "dhp48:2": "byāsattamanasaṁ naraṁ; ",
    "dhp48:3": "Atittaññeva kāmesu, ",
    "dhp48:4": "antako kurute vasaṁ. ",
    "dhp49:0": "Macchariyakosiyaseṭṭhivatthu ",
    "dhp49:1": "Yathāpi bhamaro pupphaṁ, ",
    "dhp49:2": "vaṇṇagandhamaheṭhayaṁ; ",
    "dhp49:3": "Paleti rasamādāya, ",
    "dhp49:4": "evaṁ gāme munī care. ",
    "dhp50:0": "Pāveyyaājīvakavatthu ",
    "dhp50:1": "Na paresaṁ vilomāni, ",
    "dhp50:2": "na paresaṁ katākataṁ; ",
    "dhp50:3": "Attanova avekkheyya, ",
    "dhp50:4": "katāni akatāni ca. ",
    "dhp51:0": "Chattapāṇiupāsakavatthu ",
    "dhp51:1": "Yathāpi ruciraṁ pupphaṁ, ",
    "dhp51:2": "vaṇṇavantaṁ agandhakaṁ; ",
    "dhp51:3": "Evaṁ subhāsitā vācā, ",
    "dhp51:4": "aphalā hoti akubbato. ",
    "dhp52:1": "Yathāpi ruciraṁ pupphaṁ, ",
    "dhp52:2": "Vaṇṇavantaṁ sagandhakaṁ; ",
    "dhp52:3": "Evaṁ subhāsitā vācā, ",
    "dhp52:4": "Saphalā hoti kubbato. ",
    "dhp53:0": "Visākhāvatthu ",
    "dhp53:1": "Yathāpi puppharāsimhā, ",
    "dhp53:2": "kayirā mālāguṇe bahū; ",
    "dhp53:3": "Evaṁ jātena maccena, ",
    "dhp53:4": "kattabbaṁ kusalaṁ bahuṁ. ",
    "dhp54:0": "Ānandattherapañhavatthu ",
    "dhp54:1": "Na pupphagandho paṭivātameti, ",
    "dhp54:2": "Na candanaṁ tagaramallikā vā; ",
    "dhp54:3": "Satañca gandho paṭivātameti, ",
    "dhp54:4": "Sabbā disā sappuriso pavāyati. ",
    "dhp55:1": "Candanaṁ tagaraṁ vāpi, ",
    "dhp55:2": "uppalaṁ atha vassikī; ",
    "dhp55:3": "Etesaṁ gandhajātānaṁ, ",
    "dhp55:4": "sīlagandho anuttaro. ",
    "dhp56:0": "Mahākassapattherapiṇḍapātadinnavatthu ",
    "dhp56:1": "Appamatto ayaṁ gandho, ",
    "dhp56:2": "yāyaṁ tagaracandanī; ",
    "dhp56:3": "Yo ca sīlavataṁ gandho, ",
    "dhp56:4": "vāti devesu uttamo. ",
    "dhp57:0": "Godhikattheraparinibbānavatthu ",
    "dhp57:1": "Tesaṁ sampannasīlānaṁ, ",
    "dhp57:2": "appamādavihārinaṁ; ",
    "dhp57:3": "Sammadaññāvimuttānaṁ, ",
    "dhp57:4": "māro maggaṁ na vindati. ",
    "dhp58:0": "Garahadinnavatthu ",
    "dhp58:1": "Yathā saṅkāradhānasmiṁ, ",
    "dhp58:2": "ujjhitasmiṁ mahāpathe; ",
    "dhp58:3": "Padumaṁ tattha jāyetha, ",
    "dhp58:4": "sucigandhaṁ manoramaṁ. ",
    "dhp59:1": "Evaṁ saṅkārabhūtesu, ",
    "dhp59:2": "andhabhūte puthujjane; ",
    "dhp59:3": "Atirocati paññāya, ",
    "dhp59:4": "sammāsambuddhasāvako. ",
    "dhp59:5": "Pupphavaggo catuttho. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "dhp44:0.1": "Minor Collection ",
    "dhp44:0.2": "Sayings of the Dhamma 44–59 ",
    "dhp44:0.3": "4. Flowers ",
    "dhp44:1": "Who bestirs this earth, ",
    "dhp44:2": "and the Yama realm with its gods? ",
    "dhp44:3": "Who sets out the well-taught word of truth, ",
    "dhp44:4": "as an expert a flower? ",
    "dhp45:1": "A trainee bestirs this earth, ",
    "dhp45:2": "and the Yama realm with its gods. ",
    "dhp45:3": "A trainee sets out the well-taught word of truth, ",
    "dhp45:4": "as an expert a flower. ",
    "dhp46:1": "Knowing this body’s like foam, ",
    "dhp46:2": "realizing it’s all just a mirage, ",
    "dhp46:3": "and cutting off Māra’s blossoming, ",
    "dhp46:4": "vanish from the King of Death. ",
    "dhp47:1": "As a mighty flood sweeps off a sleeping village, ",
    "dhp47:2": "death steals away a man ",
    "dhp47:3": "even as he gathers flowers, ",
    "dhp47:4": "his mind caught up in them. ",
    "dhp48:1": "The terminator gains control of the man ",
    "dhp48:2": "who has not had his fill of pleasures, ",
    "dhp48:3": "even as he gathers flowers, ",
    "dhp48:4": "his mind caught up in them. ",
    "dhp49:1": "A bee takes the nectar ",
    "dhp49:2": "and moves on, doing no damage ",
    "dhp49:3": "to the flower’s beauty and fragrance; ",
    "dhp49:4": "and that’s how a sage should walk in the village. ",
    "dhp50:1": "Don’t find fault with others, ",
    "dhp50:2": "with what they’ve done or left undone. ",
    "dhp50:3": "You should only watch yourself, ",
    "dhp50:4": "what you’ve done or left undone. ",
    "dhp51:1": "Just like a glorious flower ",
    "dhp51:2": "that’s colorful but lacks fragrance; ",
    "dhp51:3": "eloquent speech is fruitless ",
    "dhp51:4": "for one who does not act on it. ",
    "dhp52:1": "Just like a glorious flower ",
    "dhp52:2": "that’s both colorful and fragrant, ",
    "dhp52:3": "eloquent speech is fruitful ",
    "dhp52:4": "for one who acts on it. ",
    "dhp53:1": "Just as one would create many garlands ",
    "dhp53:2": "from a heap of flowers, ",
    "dhp53:3": "when a person has come to be born, ",
    "dhp53:4": "they should do many skillful things. ",
    "dhp54:1": "The fragrance of flowers doesn’t spread upwind, ",
    "dhp54:2": "nor sandalwood, pinwheel, or jasmine; ",
    "dhp54:3": "but the fragrance of the good spreads upwind; ",
    "dhp54:4": "a true person’s virtue spreads in every direction. ",
    "dhp55:1": "Among all the fragrances—",
    "dhp55:2": "sandalwood or pinwheel ",
    "dhp55:3": "or lotus or jasmine—",
    "dhp55:4": "the fragrance of virtue is supreme. ",
    "dhp56:1": "Faint is the fragrance ",
    "dhp56:2": "of sandal or pinwheel; ",
    "dhp56:3": "but the fragrance of the virtuous ",
    "dhp56:4": "floats to the highest gods. ",
    "dhp57:1": "For those accomplished in ethics, ",
    "dhp57:2": "meditating diligently, ",
    "dhp57:3": "freed through the highest knowledge, ",
    "dhp57:4": "Māra cannot find their path. ",
    "dhp58:1": "From a heap of trash ",
    "dhp58:2": "discarded on the highway, ",
    "dhp58:3": "a lotus might blossom, ",
    "dhp58:4": "fragrant and delightful. ",
    "dhp59:1": "So too, among those thought of as trash, ",
    "dhp59:2": "a disciple of the perfect Buddha ",
    "dhp59:3": "outshines with their wisdom ",
    "dhp59:4": "the blind ordinary folk. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "dhp44:1": "imaṁ → komaṁ (mr) | vicessati → vijessati (sya-all, pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
    "dhp44:4": "pupphamiva pacessati → pupphamivappacessati (pts2ed, mr) ",
    "dhp46:3": "papupphakāni → sapupphakāni (ṭīkā) ",
    "dhp47:2": "byāsattamanasaṁ → byāsattamānasaṁ (mr) ",
    "dhp49:2": "vaṇṇagandhamaheṭhayaṁ → vaṇṇagandhaṁ aheṭhayaṁ (bj, pts1ed, pts2ed); vaṇṇavantaṁ agandhakaṁ (cck); vaṇṇavantaṁ aheṭhayaṁ (sya1ed, sya2ed); vaṇṇagandhamapoṭhayaṁ (mr) ",
    "dhp52:2": "sagandhakaṁ → sugandhakaṁ (csp1ed thag5.2:5 [Subhūtattheragāthā]) ",
    "dhp52:4": "hoti kubbato → pakubbato (bj); sukubbato (sya-all, km); sakubbato (pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
    "dhp54:2": "tagaramallikā → taggaramallikā (csp1ed) ",
    "dhp56:2": "yāyaṁ tagaracandanī → yvāyaṁ tagaracandanī (sya-all); yvāyaṁ tagaracandanaṁ (csp1ed) ",
    "dhp58:1": "saṅkāradhānasmiṁ → saṅkāraṭhānasmiṁ (mr) ",
    "dhp59:2": "andhabhūte → andhībhūte (mr) "
  },
